kancolletool (0.8.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fleet status display (accounts for expeditions and baths/repairs)
  * Expedition notifications
  * Ctrl+<num> switches tab, <num> on the Fleets page switches fleet
  * Smaller font sizes and margins to make sure all names fit
  * Construction notifications now only name the new ship if the Spoiler box is checked (Closes: #18)
  * Fixes a few crashes caused by race conditions and null pointer dereferences
  * Fixes incorrect handling of instant repairs (notifications still fired) (Closes: #17)

